Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}\NWill be abolished socially when we realize that we are all one species\NUnder the sun instead of weapons of mass destruction

Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5}\NWe unleash weapons of mass creation\NYou must elevate your mind to a higher state of spiritual awareness

